This is the most delicious dish I've had a long time. I didn't have all the ingredients so I substituted applesauce, 1/4 onion, and spicy brown mustard then servced it over brown basmati rice. It was fabulous! I'm anxious to try the recipe as written. I'll bet it's even better.

