Rating: 2
Carole from Rhode Island- The apple slices on top of each ham was delicious. I did not slice ham in quarters but in half. After reducing juice, etc.by half, I found it to be a little too thick. Sauce was sweet. I would make this again but just with the apples slices between ham. The apples gave the ham a good flavor after being in the oven @250 for about l0 min.

